👋 Hi, I’m @LiceBusters
👀 I’m passionate about helping families stay lice-free with safe, non-toxic lice removal treatments.
🌱 I’m constantly improving our methods and staying updated on the best lice removal practices to provide fast and effective relief.
💞️ I’m looking to collaborate with schools, camps, and community groups to prevent lice outbreaks and provide educational resources.
📫 How to reach me: You can reach me at info@licebusters.org or through our website at [licebusters.org](https://licebusters.org).
😄 Pronouns: We/Us (team)
⚡ Fun fact: We've helped over 10,000 families get rid of lice in a safe, gentle, and affordable way!
